      <title>大众汽车及其中国合作伙伴上汽集团因销量下滑将关闭工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/vw-and-china-partner-saic-set-to-close-car-plant-as-sales-shrink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车集团及其历史最悠久的中国合作伙伴计划关闭中国一家工厂，甚至可能关闭更多工厂，以应对内燃机汽车需求放缓的问题。这是继合资公司第一家工厂停止生产后，大众汽车集团进一步撤出中国业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/vw-and-china-partner-saic-set-to-close-car-plant-as-sales-shrink</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 12:20:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南废除股票预融资规则，着眼于市场升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/vietnam-scraps-stock-pre-funding-rule-paving-way-for-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南将取消海外投资者对股票交易进行全额预先融资的要求，这是该国为增加被重新归类为新兴市场的机会而做出的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/vietnam-scraps-stock-pre-funding-rule-paving-way-for-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 10:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
